sequenceDiagram
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails<br/>Orchestrator
    participant BuiltIn as Built-in Detector<br/>8080/TCP HTTP plaintext
    participant Istio as Istio Sidecar<br/>mTLS STRICT
    participant HF as HuggingFace Detector<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Judge as LLM Judge Detector<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant S3 as S3/MinIO<br/>9000/TCP HTTP
    participant vLLM as External vLLM Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Note over Orchestrator,BuiltIn: Flow 1: Built-in Detection (co-deployed)
    Orchestrator->>BuiltIn: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP plaintext, No Auth<br/>detector_params: regex/file_type/custom
    BuiltIn-->>Orchestrator: Detection Results<br/>[{detection, detection_type, score}]

    Note over Orchestrator,HF: Flow 2: HuggingFace Model Inference
    Note over S3,HF: (Init) KServe Storage Initializer
    S3-->>HF: Model Weights Download<br/>9000/TCP, AWS credentials
    Orchestrator->>Istio: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP
    Istio->>HF: Forward Request<br/>mTLS (Istio), KServe auth
    HF->>HF: Model Inference<br/>(AutoModelForSequenceClassification<br/>or GraniteForCausalLM)
    HF-->>Istio: Classification Results
    Istio-->>Orchestrator: Response<br/>mTLS

    Note over Orchestrator,vLLM: Flow 3: LLM Judge Evaluation
    Orchestrator->>Istio: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>or /api/v1/text/generation
    Istio->>Judge: Forward Request<br/>mTLS (Istio), KServe auth
    Judge->>vLLM: OpenAI-compatible API call<br/>VLLM_BASE_URL, HTTP
    vLLM-->>Judge: LLM Evaluation Response
    Judge-->>Istio: Evaluation Results<br/>[{detection, detection_type, score}]
    Istio-->>Orchestrator: Response<br/>mTLS
